135
00:21:50,189 --> 00:21:52,432
the Metta Sutta.

136
00:21:52,452 --> 00:21:57,823
If you are wise and want to reach the state of peace, you should behave like this.

137
00:21:57,863 --> 00:22:03,472
You should be upright, responsible, gentle and humble.

138
00:22:04,414 --> 00:22:09,143
You should be easily contented and need only a few things.

139
00:22:10,134 --> 00:22:11,878
You should not always be busy.

140
00:22:12,681 --> 00:22:15,567
You should have the right sort of work.

141
00:22:16,529 --> 00:22:19,656
Your senses should be controlled and you should be modest.

142
00:22:20,839 --> 00:22:25,832
You should not be exclusively attached to only a few people.

143
00:22:25,811 --> 00:22:31,958
You should not do the slightest thing that a wise person could blame you for.

144
00:22:31,978 --> 00:22:35,442
You should always be thinking, may all beings be happy.

145
00:22:36,343 --> 00:22:53,759
Whatever living beings there are, be they weak or strong, big or small, large or slender, living nearby or far away, those who have already been born and those who have yet to be born.

146
00:22:54,262 --> 00:22:58,730
May all beings without exception be happy.

147
00:22:58,750 --> 00:23:00,692
You should not tell lies to each other.

148
00:23:00,732 --> 00:23:05,579
Do not think that anyone anywhere is of no value.

149
00:23:07,363 --> 00:23:11,087
Do not wish harm to anyone, not even when you are angry.

150
00:23:12,069 --> 00:23:23,105
Just as a mother would protect her only child at the risk of her own life, so you should let the warmth of your heart go out to all beings.

151
00:23:24,317 --> 00:23:31,463
Let your thoughts of love go through the whole world with no ill will and no hate.

152
00:23:31,483 --> 00:23:41,553
Whether you are standing, walking, sitting or lying down, so long as you are awake, you should develop this mindfulness.

153
00:23:42,815 --> 00:23:47,298
This, they say, is the noblest way to live.

154
00:23:47,318 --> 00:23:53,463
And if you do not fall into bad ways, but live well and develop insight,

155
00:23:53,696 --> 00:24:03,232
and are no longer attached to all the desires of the senses, then truly you will never need to be reborn in this world again.

156
00:24:04,454 --> 00:24:13,950
So we can make our way to the Marquis.

157
00:25:40,397 --> 00:25:41,718
Thank you.

